== English ==
=== Etymology ===
Eponymous of king Pyrrhus of Epirus, who suffered heavy losses while defeating the Romans.

==== Adjective ====
'''Pyrrhic'''
# a very costly [[victory]]; a victory in which the means [[outweigh]] the ends

